<h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
  About
</h2>

<div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow sm:rounded-lg mt-8">
  <div class="px-4 py-5 sm:p-6 text-gray-900">
    <p>
      <strong>petakopi</strong> is an answer for coffee lovers looking for a
      new place to have coffee. We don't intend it to be another Google Place,
      Foursquare, Instagram or others. We just want to find a place to have a
      good coffee for now.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-2">
      That being said, we are still open to the idea of helping the community.
      But time is limited so, new features will be added slowly, like a
      dripping coffee from a V60.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-2">
      If you think this is something you like and want to help with, you can start by
      submitting local coffee shops you know right now. The code is also available
      publicly at this
      <a href="https://github.com/amree/petakopi" target="_blank" class="font-medium text-brown-600 hover:text-brown-500">repository</a>.
      Feel free to send some code there if you can.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-2">
